Human Resource Officer‎
Catcokids
-
Karachi
· Recruitment, conduct interviews, selection, induction, orientation of all center level staff
· Review and update Job Descriptions for center staff in coordination with HR regional team
· Identify current and future staffing needs at centers
· Monitor the HR performance of all center staff
· Keep liaison with recruitment agencies, local organizations, educational institutions, etc within the region.
· Recommended employee’s for promotions
Skills Required:
• HR documentation (appointment letters, employee contracts, confirmation, warning, commendation, termination, promotion, transfer, experience, legal notices, Process Exit/ termination of employee etc.)
• Coordination for Quarterly Performance Evaluations of all Staff
• Ensure Annual Medical check-up of staff
• Employee services and counseling when required
• Maintain Employee Attendance / Leave Record
• Employee Personal files maintenance
• Employee Detail Record Database maintenance
• Documentation and updating in relevant files
